Behavior
----
As with the commands, you also add another feature. Terminal commands. All terminal commands are best ran using python to run them with bash. To use the terminal its "<prefix> term <text to send to bash>" and you output the result of the terminal.
Aswell as a terminal, powershell commands can be ran with "<prefix> pwrshl <text to run through powershell>" and you output the result of powershell.
